{
  "stem": "11472.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was under the bed with three other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe there were 15 people, 20 people, yeah, because there was the [NON-ENGLISH] family and the [NON-ENGLISH] family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In that direction of the-- they did not-- in that direction of the bunkers, they didn't go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened was [SIGHS] they came on our side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they saw people, so they stopped at that side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is my grandmother went out to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, the other people, I don't know, their bunker, they-- they didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or maybe they hid themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My uncle Shulim, the one that did all these excavation, tried to get through to-- because those bunkers were made.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He knew that he could push through a wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got stuck in that wall, and he had a nervous shock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My aunt Yetta, and my aunt Chana were also under the bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Sharma was under the bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], that people-- and other people were starting to come out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm laying on the bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Herr [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH] went out, and I'm still laying under the bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hear my aunt Yetta saying, [NON-ENGLISH]-- they used to call me Shunia at home, like an endearment, you know-- Sonia would be Shunia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], where are you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I'm here, Yetta.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, why didn't you come out?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said, I'm afraid-- they took my mother away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, don't worry, Shunia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever will happen to me will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't worry, I'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father is in town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He thinks that we're safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we thought that they took them out immediately and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we have to open up a big exit.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
